@startuml akdb-main-activity
title ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB - Main Activity
start
:Select project and backend;
if (DB-native architecture change?) then (yes)
  :Create/update SAD sections, decisions and UML
through CLI, API or MCP;
  :Persist canonical akdb:// records;
  :Validate completeness and traceability;
  :Export deterministic docs/architecture projection;
else (external evidence)
  :Register repository or import documents;
  :Scan/read source without repository mutation;
endif
:Search, recall, reason or build context pack;
if (Drift detected?) then (yes)
  :Report source-anchored finding;
endif
if (Downstream consumer needs projection?) then (yes)
  :Consume exported SAD/UML files;
endif
stop
@enduml
